General.Name: CoinWorksCoin
General.Description: CoinWorksCoin was an experimental coin running off multiple algorithms like Quarkcoin. With both the twitter feed and the website down there isn't much information on this particular crypto currency.

ICO.Description:
Bringing Bonds to Blockchain. Labrys are developing the technology needed to effectively issue bonds as tokenised assets directly on the blockchain. By utilising the latest technology available, inefficiencies in the issuance process are able to be eliminated, creating a much more efficient and cost effective bond ecosystem. LAB tokens allow the user to gain ownership of a bond and provides interest payments.

The Labrys ICO has been delayed to a TBA date.. The ICO token allocation represents 75% of the total supply and will be available for a 0.10 USD price. Users will be able to participate with ETH.

Token Reserve Split (25%):

  • 15%: Labrys founding team allocation
    10%: Company reserve
